<A HREF="about.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/information_header.gif" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP border = none alt = "Information Request Form"></A>
<p>
</center>

<font size = +1>Welcome to <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> Product Information Request Form.  Complete this form to be mailed product information with a referral to your local Proxima representative.<p>

Or, for immediate assistance, call our Info and Support Hotline:
<CENTER><table>
<tr>
	<TD WIDTH=200><CENTER>
		<FONT SIZE=+2>800-447-7692</FONT><br>
		U.S. and Canada</CENTER>
	</td>
	<td><CENTER>
		Europe: +44-1628-481555 ext. 207<br>
		Other Locations: 619-457-5500</CENTER>
	</td>
</tr>
</table></CENTER></font>
