<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>What is Multimedia Desktop Projection</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor="FFFFFF" vlink="AF0040" alink="04BC04">

<center> 
<A HREF="university.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/what_is_header.gif" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP border = none alt = "What is Multimedia Projection"></A>
</center>

<p>
<IMG SRC="gifs/desktop_logo.gif" align = left hspace = 8 vspace = 8 width = 84 height = 105>
<H3>What is Multimedia Projection:</H3>
<p>
Multimedia projection is the process of displaying computer based information on a large screen to facilitate group communication.  By combining the benefits of large screen projection with the power of the computer, multimedia projection offers the same increase in productivity to workgroups that personal computers give to individuals.<br>
<IMG SRC="gifs/meeting_picture.gif" align = right hspace = 8>
<p>
<B>Using Multimedia Projection for Meetings</B>
<br>
Multimedia Projection makes your meetings more productive by allowing everyone to simultaneously view and work with computer based information. Group projects such as scheduling and budgeting can be displayed, reviewed, and finalized in a single meeting. Full group participation builds consensus and ensures that the final result has everyone's support.<br clear = all>
<IMG SRC="gifs/presentation_picture.gif" align = left hspace = 8>
<p>
<B>Using Multimedia Projection for Powerful Presentations</B><BR>
Multimedia projection is an extremely effective communication tool. Plug a Proxima multimedia projection system into your computer to present everything from simple charts and graphics to complex animation and video.
<p>
The result is a dynamic multimedia experience that standard overhead, slide, or flip chart presentations can't match.
<p>
By creating the your presentation directly on the computer - using the software you are already familiar with-you save the time and expense of creating overheads, slides, and other presentation materials.<br clear = all>
<p>
<H3>Multimedia Projection Benefits:</H3>
<p>
<B>More Efficient</B>
<br>
Multimedia projection is faster and less expensive than producing slides or transparencies.
<p>
<B>More Effective</B><BR>
Multimedia projection has superior image quality and the possibility of integration of sound and motion can let you make more compelling presentations.
<p>
<B>More Convenient</B><BR>
Changing your message on the fly is easy with today's feature rich software.
<p>
<B>More Responsive</B><BR>
Combined with our Cyclops&reg; command and control systems, you can  change and adapt your presentations with ease.
<p>

<center>
[&#160 <A HREF="university.html">Presenters University</A>&#160 |&#160 
<A HREF="../Solving/solving.html">Support And Service</A>&#160 |&#160 
<A HREF="../Partnering/partnering.html">Resellers Forum</A>&#160 ]
