   <title>Proxima Technical Support - Cable Reference</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<A NAME="TOP"></A>
<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML//EN">
<center>
<A HREF="solving.map"><IMG SRC="jpgs/header.jpg" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP border = none alt = "Support And Services"></A>
<p>
<b><font COLOR="#0000A0"><font SIZE=+3>Cable Reference</font>
<br><FONT SIZE=-2>Last modified: 1/29/97</FONT></font></b>
<hr>
</center>
<center>
<TABLE>
<tr><td width=500>
<B>INSTRUCTIONS:</B> Clicking on a product will take you to that product.  
Clicking on an underlined cable part number below will download a cable diagram in Adobe PDF format.  
<p>To obtain Adobe Acrobat Reader click here:  <A HREF="http://www.adobe.com/acrobat/readstep.html"><IMG SRC="gifs/acrobat_logo.gif" WIDTH=88 HEIGHT=31 ALIGN=middle></A>
<p>
To order a cable, contact a local Proxima authorized reseller.  For a listing of resellers near you, please call Proxima at 800-447-7694, option 1.
</td>
</tr>
</table></center>
<p>
