<table width = 596>
	<tr>
		<td><B>PROXIMA INFORMATION:</B><br>
<font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Corporation is a leading designer, developer, manufacturer and marketer of liquid crystal display (LCD) projectors and panels for display of computer and video images for convenient viewing by groups. Desktop Projection products account for more than 90 percent of the Company's sales.  <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> video projection products for PC, Macintosh, and workstation based market are made to he highest standards of quality and reliability, ensuring that the image you project will look its best.
