<p>
<font size = "+1"><font color = "BF0000"><B>EZTools</B></font> is a floating toolbar that, in combination with the EZPresenter VGA PC Card, allows you to use your notebook computer's display independently of the audience's display. This means PowerPoint can be in slide show mode on the audience display and slide sorter mode on the notebook's display simultaneously! You can preview your presentation, read prepared notes from the computer display, and even step into another application momentarily, all without your audience seeing any changes, unless you want them to. With a single click, you can link the two screens for simultaneous display. Click again to unlink them and return to your private screen.</font>
<p>

