<p>
<font size = "+1"><font color = "BF0000"><B>SmartSuite</B></font> includes five of the hardest-working, easiest-to-use applications in business today--Lotus 1-2-3 spreadsheet, Lotus Word Pro word processor, Lotus Approach relational database, Lotus Freelance Graphics presentation graphics, and Lotus Organizer personal and group scheduling software. SmartSuite also includes Lotus ScreenCam, the screen and sound capture utility that lets you create custom audio/visual communications.
<p>
SmartSuite is packed with productivity tools that help you work smarter. From Lotus SmartCenter, your SmartSuite command center, it's easy to store and access applications, files, e-mail, the Internet, help services, and more.
<p>
Lotus SmartMasters are a series of easy-to-use, pre-designed templates that give you a head start on all kinds of everyday business tasks. And  with features like TeamConsolidate, TeamReview, and TeamMail, SmartSuite gives you some new exciting ways to collaborate with your colleagues, co-workers, and associates. So whether you1re working by yourself or as a team, SmartSuite, all by itself or together with Lotus Notes, is designed to help your business be more efficient.</font>
<br clear = right>
<br>
<table cellspacing = 0 cellpadding = 3 border = 1>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><B>Features:</B></td>
		<td valign = top><UL><LI> Use Lotus SmartCenter to store and access applications, files, e-mail, the Internet, help services, and more.<br>
<LI> With built-in connections to the Internet and special offers from CompuServe and Global Network Navigator, you can actually surf the Net free!<br>
<LI> Freelance Graphics makes publishing presentations to the World Wide Web easier than ever.<br>
<LI> Lotus SmartMasters are easy-to-use, predesigned templates that give you a headstart on all kinds of everyday business tasks.<br>
<LI> The InfoBox lets you choose fonts, colors, and other attributes.<br>
<LI> Fast Format lets you duplicate attributes all in one</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><B>Price:</B></td>
