		<td valign = top>IBM PC or compatible (80486 or higher); VGA adapter and monitor, mouse or other pointing device, 3.52 high density disk drive (CD  ROM drive for CD ROM version); Windows 95; 8 MB RAM minimum (12 MB recommended when running more than one application); 57 MB hard disk space for minimum installation.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
