<br clear = all>
<br>
<font size = "+1"><font color = "BF0000"><B>Creator</B></font> is a software multimedia presentation package for MS Windows with more features than systems at ten times the cost. Creator combines functionality and flexibility in a point and click interface requiring no programming knowledge.
<IMG SRC="gifs/microvitec1.gif" width = 155 height = 162 alt = "Photo of MicroVitec Multimedia Product" align = right hspace = 6>
<p>
The Creator interface allows swift planning and implementation of interactive multimedia presentations using images, text, branching, animation, video and audio--plus a huge range of template backdrops to save you time in preparation. Also included in every Creator package is a free CD-ROM packed with sample graphics, MIDI, WAV and AVI files to give your multimedia presentation that extra buzz. With over 50 different types of fades, dissolves, and effects (100 with <font color = "BF0000"><B>Creator Professional</B></font>), Creator will enable you to hold your audience's attention. Add the multiple audio tracks, and you now have a multiple language presentation.
<p>
Creator provides access to 95% of the screen area by using floating tools that are only on the screen when you need them. Move from text to video, and the text tool is automatically replaced by the video tool. When your presentation is finished, you can publish it to disk using the royalty free run time Creator publisher that will allow your audience to review your presentation over and over again.
<p>
Creator is the answer to true Multimedia presentations, but don't take our word for it--contact us today for your free Creator demo disk.</font>
<br clear = right>
<br>
<table cellspacing = 0 cellpadding = 3 border = 1>
	<tr>
