<LI> Escape key disable (Creator Professional)
<LI> Multiple audio tracks
<LI> End-user definable slide shows
<LI> Royalty free runtime publisher
<LI> Over 50 different fades, wipes, and effects included (100 in Creator  Professional) Windows 3.X and 95 compatible</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><B>Price:</B></td>
		<td valign = top>Creator $249.00 MSRP<br>
Special Proxima offer $99.00 (UK &#163;66.00)<br>
Creator Professional $499.00 MSRP<br>
Special Proxima offer $249.00 (UK &#163;170.00)</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><B>Requirements:</B></td>
		<td valign = top>Windows 3.1, 3.11, 95; 386 SX (486 recommended); 4 MB RAM (8 MB recommended); 12 MB of available hard disk space.</td>
	</tr>
