<p>
<font size = "+1">The <font color = "BF0000"><B>Macintosh PowerBook 5300c/100</B></font> provides the high performance of PowerPC processor technology and a bright, active-matrix color display--ideal for graphics or presentations. The PowerBook 5300c/100 supports color video-out and 16-bit CD-quality stereo sound output.
<p>
<IMG SRC="gifs/apple1.gif" width = 166 height = 146 align = right hspace = 9>
<p>
Featuring an advanced 100-megahertz PowerPC 603e processor, the PowerBook 5300c/100 lets mobile users experience the true power of desktop computing--all in a system that weighs only 6.2 pounds.
<p>
Already powerful, the PowerBook 5300c/100 is designed to make expansion easy. You can expand the memory to 64 megabytes. The PowerBook 5300c/100 also features two PC Card slots as well as an expansion bay for third-party solutions.
<p>
Because communication is so vital to mobile users, the PowerBook 5300c/100 offers a range of networking and communications capabilities. Through its PC Card slots, you can add a wired or wireless modem, storage, or Ethernet networking capability.
<p>
With its power, expandability, and high-quality color active-matrix display, the PowerBook 5300c/100 is a portable computer that truly doesn't compromise on quality and capability.
