<IMG SRC="gifs/ti5200.gif" width = 230 height = 233 alt = "Photo of TravelMate 5200 Notebook" align = right hspace = 9>
<font size = "+1">Texas Instruments built its reputation on high-performance notebook computers - and now the <font color = "BF0000"><B>TravelMate 5200</B></font> pushes the boundaries of notebook performance even further, with a sizzling fast 120MHz Pentium processor that brings new power to notebook computing. The TravelMate 5200 includes 256KB Level 2 cache with PCI bus architecture to ensure the utmost in Pentium processor power and connectivity.
<p>
The TravelMate 5200 features an all-new 11.3" SuperVGA active matrix display that shows up to 65,000 simultaneous colors, for incredibly rich, vivid color. Other standard features include a 1.2 gigabyte hard disk drive with a standard 8MB of memory, a serial infrared port for wireless connections, and a PCMCIA Type III card slot. Two lithium ion batteries and an intelligent battery system deliver exceptional battery life, in the award-winning tradition of the TravelMate 5000 Series.
<p>
With its combination of power and capabilities, the TravelMate 5200 delivers true desktop performance in a notebook computer that weighs just 6.7 pounds. For even greater flexibility, choose from one of TI's DockMate docking systems. The TravelMate 5200 gives you the convenience of both Windows 95 and Windows for Workgroups, so you can keep your options open and protect your investment, both today and tomorrow.</font>
<br clear = right>
<br>
<table cellspacing = 0 cellpadding = 3 border = 1>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><B>Features:</B></td>
		<td valign = top><UL>
<LI>Electrifying Speed:  120MHz Pentium processor with PCI bus and 256 KB level 2 cache
<LI>Dazzling Display: 11.3" Super VGA active matrix
<LI>Outstanding Battery Life: Intelligent battery system with two lithium ion batteries
<LI>Integrated Multimedia: 16-bit sound card, internal speaker, and microphone
<LI>Software Flexibility: Pre-installed with both Windows 95 and Windows for Workgroups</td>
	</tr>
</table>
<p>

