<HEAD>
<TITLE> Presentation Resource Center - Extron Electronics </TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor="FFFFFF" vlink = "AF0040" alink="04BC04">

<center> 
<A HREF="univ_resource.map"><IMG SRC="../gifs/resource_header.gif" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP   border = none alt = "Presentation Resource Center"></A>
</center>

<p>
<IMG SRC="gifs/extron_logo.gif" width = 216 height = 33 alt = "Extron Electronics Logo" align = left hspace = 9 vspace = 9>
<table cellspacing = 0 cellpadding = 3>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><font size = "+1"><B>Company:</B></td>
		<td valign = top><font size = "+1"><font color = "BF0000"><B>Extron Electronics</B></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><B>Address:</B></td>
		<td valign = top>1230 South Lewis Street<br>Anaheim, CA 92805</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><B>Phone Sales:</B></td>
		<td valign = top>(714) 491-1500</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top><B>WWW:</B></td>
		<td valign = top><A HREF="http://www.extron.com">http://www.extron.com</A></td>
	</tr>
</table>
<p>
<font size = "+1">Extron Electronics is a manufacturer of computer-video interfaces, switchers, distribution amplifiers, high resolution cables, and computer to video scan converters.
<IMG SRC="gifs/extron2.gif" width = 216 height = 160 alt = "Photo of Extron Electronics Cables" align = right hspace = 9>
<p>
<font color = "BF0000"><B>High resolution VGA extension cables</B></font> allow the outputs of the P/2 DA 2 Plus, P/2 DA 4, and P/2 DA 6 to be extended to lengths up to 250 feet utilizing min-coax cables.
<p>
<font color = "BF0000"><B>High resolution Macintosh extension cables</B></font> are used to connect Macintosh computers to data monitors or projectors or to extend the length of the output form the mac 2 DA 2.
<p>
VGA and Macintosh termination adapters are designed to emulate a local computer monitor for use with laptop applications.
<p>
Mac/VGA adapters are used to convert a Macintosh computer output to a VGA configuration for input to VGA devices.</font>
<p>
<B>Display Products:</B>
<menu>
<table border=1>
	<tr>			
		<td>P/2 DA 2 Plus, a one input, two output VGA distribution amplifier (150MHz)</td>
		<td>$265.00</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>P/2 DA 2 LC, a one input, two output VGA distribution amplifier (100MHz)</td>
		<td>$185.00</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>Mac II DA 2, a one input, two output Macintosh distribution amplifier</td>
		<td>$250.00</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>SW2, 4, 6 VGA, a 2, 4, or 6 input to one output Macintosh switcher</td>
		<td>various</td>
	</tr>
