                <TD WIDTH=205 align = center>325.1</TD>
        </TR>
</TABLE>

<P>
<LI><B>Does the Desktop Projector 2700 have audio capability?</B>  
<P>
No, the 2700 does not have audio capability.
<P>
<LI><B>Can the internal speakers on the Desktop Projector 2XXX be disabled?</B>   
<P>
No, the internal speakers on the Desktop Projector 2XXX can not be disabled.
<P>
<LI><B>Can a Desktop Projector 2700/2800 be upgraded to a 2710/2810?</B>   
<P>
The 2710/2810 projector has a different LCD panel, mirrors and other components.  There is not an upgrade from the 2700/2800 to the 2710/2810.  
</OL>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
