<HEAD> 

<TITLE> Field Note: #36 </TITLE>

</HEAD>



<BODY bgcolor = "#ffffff">



<center>

<A HREF="solving.map"><IMG SRC="jpgs/header.jpg" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP border = none alt = "Support And Services"></A>

<H2>Field Note:  #36</H2>

</center>



<P>

September 6, 1994

<P>

Subject:  Substitute Lens for 8300/8400 Projector

<P>

Field Note: #36

<P>

<U><B>PROBLEM

</B></U>

<P>

In certain installations, customers have indicated that the original

8300/8400 zoom lens is inadequate to display the image size desired.

<P>

<U><B>DISCUSSION

</B></U>

<P>

The installed lens in the 8300/8400 does not produce the desired image

size for a given distance in specific fixed installations.  In

these instances, a wide angle or different zoom lens would produce

the desired image size.

<P>

<U><B>SOLUTION

</B></U>

<P>

BUHL Optical has a selection of wide-angle and zoom lenses that

can replace the original lens in the 8300/8400.  For information, contact:

<P>

Joe Pentavalle<BR>

BUHL Optical Company<BR>

1009 Beech Avenue<BR>

Pittsburgh, PA  15233-2035<BR>

FAX: (412)322-2640<BR>

TEL: (412)321-0076<p>

<BR>

<center>
