<HEAD>
<TITLE> Resellers Forum - Why Partner with Proxima? </TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor="FFFFFF" vlink="AF0040" alink="04BC04">

<center>
<A HREF="partnering_pc.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/partnering_header.gif" border = none width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP  alt = "Public Resellers Forum"></A>
<p>
</center>

<table width = 594>
	<tr>
		<td colspan = 2 align = center><font color = "135F13"><H2>Tap Into The Multi-Billion Dollar<br>Multimedia Projection Market.</H2></font></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan = 2><font size = +1>In today's fast-changing computer market, end-users like nothing better than leveraging their investment in technology. Anytime you can help customers maximize the benefits of the computers they already own, you win. For VARs, system integrators and resellers of computer accessories and peripherals, that's why <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font><sup><font size = "-1">&reg;</font></sup> <A HREF="../Solutions/solutions.html">Multimedia Projection<sup><font size = "-2">TM</font></sup> products</A> present a golden opportunity.
<p>
<IMG SRC="gifs/emerging.gif" align = right width = "90" height = "100" hspace = 6 alt = "An Emerging Billion...">Corporations, government, and education spend more than $1 billion on Multimedia Projection products per year. The future market for projectors and LCD panels is expected to expand to more than $2.5 billion. At the head of the pack in this explosive industry, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> is well-positioned to capitalize on this phenomenal growth rate, with a family of innovative Multimedia Projection solutions designed to meet every need and budget.
<p>
Enabling users to project computer screen contents up on the wall in crisp, clear color, and with options like stereo sound and integrated video, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Multimedia Projectors provide valuable benefits to customers in a variety of markets, including the following:</font><p></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top>
<IMG SRC="gifs/diamond.gif" hspace = 9 align = left><font size = +1>Training and education</font><p>
<IMG SRC="gifs/diamond.gif" hspace = 9 align = left><font size = +1>Sales force automation</font><p>
<IMG SRC="gifs/diamond.gif" hspace = 9 align = left><font size = +1>Mobile professionals</font><p></td>
			<td valign = top>
<IMG SRC="gifs/diamond.gif" hspace = 9 align = left><font size = +1>Video conferencing</font><p>
<IMG SRC="gifs/diamond.gif" hspace = 9 align = left><font size = +1>Multimedia presentations</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan = 2><IMG SRC="gifs/chart1.gif" hspace = 9><p></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan = 2><font size = +1><B>There's Always a Market<br>for Better Communication</B>
<p>
With the glut of information in the world today, anything that enhances communication is a hot commodity. That's why <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Multimedia Projection products are selling so well, to presenters, trainers, mobile computing professionals, collaborative workgroups and many others. Dynamic, reliable and easy to use, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Multimedia Projection products help these professionals get their message across more quickly and more effectively, by delivering any kind of content in a compelling, high-impact way.
<p>
By facilitating better communication, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> products yield tangible benefits for both presenters and audiences alike.
<p>
<br>
<B>Real Customers, Sharing Real<br>
Bottom-line Results</B>
<p>
Why is <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Multimedia Projection technology such a great training tool? Because it allows training to work in real time. The data projected onto the screen or wall is what's running on the presenter's computer, so it can be updated instantly. Using Multimedia Projection for training, since it requires ntohing more than a room big enough to hold all the participants. That makes it cost-effective too. 
<p> 
<IMG SRC="gifs/saved.gif" align = left valign=bottom width = "108" height = "135" hspace = 12 alt = "We've saved tens of...">
"We've saved tens of thousands of dollars by not having to produce slides," said <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> customer Derrick Hankerson, information services trainer for Blockbuster Entertainment. Rather than printing thousands of handouts or slides, Blockbuster's training department uses <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Desktop Projectors to present software programs and other training materials developed in Microsoft PowerPoint.
<br clear=all>
<p>

<B>Expanding The Possibilities</B>
<p>
Suppose you could make changes to a sales presentation while you discuss it, then close it and show your audience a video clip of how your product is being used. Or collaborate with colleagues on design reviews. Think of how you could gain consensus more quickly and reduce the number of meetings (!) by actually getting work done when you do meet. You can do all of these things with <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> Desktop Projection products.
<p>
In many companies, groupware applications like Lotus Notes and Microsoft Solutions for Workgroups are becoming an essential part of doing business. At the same time, nearly everyone is establishing a presence on the Internet. Across virtually all industries, more and more computers are linked together in both local-and wide-area networks. As this trend accelerates, the ability to project the contents of your computer screen-including Internet data or even a video conference hook-up with a satellite office- will become more and more useful.
<p>
Perfectly aligned with this trend, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Multimedia Projection technology changes the way people work together.  And the possibilities truly are limitless.
<p>
<br>
<IMG SRC="gifs/pie_graph.gif" align=right valign=top WIDTH="245" HEIGHT="212">
<B>Your Current Customers<br>
Are Showing The Way</B> 
<p>
Multimedia Projection is moving rapidly into the mainstream-and onto your customers' list of essential tools, both in the office and on the road.
<p>
By offering <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> products before your competition does, you can maintain your vital position as leading edge solution provider to your customers.
<p>
<br>
<B>A Natural Fit</B>
<p>
<font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Multimedia Projector<sup><font size = "-2">TM</font></sup> models include these user and dealer-friendly features:</font><br></td>
	</tr>
</table>
<table width = 594>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top align = right><IMG SRC="gifs/diamond.gif" hspace = 9></td>
