	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top align = right><IMG SRC="gifs/diamond.gif" hspace = 9></td>
		<td><font size = "+1">Ease of use for minimized learning curve and user support</font></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign = top align = right><IMG SRC="gifs/diamond.gif" hspace = 9></td>
		<td><font size = "+1">Superb image quality and brightness in a meeting room or on the road<p></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan = 2><font size = "+1">Flexible and easy to use, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> products allow VARs and dealers to offer a total solution that makes your customers' presentations come to life.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
<table width = 594>
	<tr>
		<td colspan = 2><font color = "236F23"><H2>Tap Into The Multi-Billion Dollar<br>Multimedia Projection Market.</H2></font></td>
