</font><p></td>
	</tr>
  <tr>
		<td colspan = 2><font color = "236F23"><H2>Proxima Supports<br>You Six Powerful Ways</H2></font></td>
	</tr>
 <tr>
    <td colspan=2><font size = +1><B>Free 10-Day Evaluation Program.</B><P>
Your qualified prospects can take home a <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> unit to try for 10 days, absolutely free. There's no risk or obligation. Experience proves that hands-on trial dramatically increases end-user demand for <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> products and helps close more sales.
<p>
<B>Pre-Sale Support</B>
<p>
<font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Account Representatives are available to help and advise you through the pre-sale process. We provide winning sales tips, configuration support, and competitive information to help you tap into a market that's a billion dollars and growing fast.
<p>
<B>Demo Purchase Program</B>
<p>Watch sales sizzle when you own your own demo unit.
<p>
We're offering great discounts on <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> products when you purchase them for demonstration purposes. Plus, VIP Program members qualify for even greater discounts.
<p>
Some of these special purchase units may be refurbished, and they're all covered by <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> one-year parts warranty. There's a limit of one unit per location, and products may not be exchanged or returned for credit. Prices are in U.S. dollars and are subject to change without notice.
