Call and order your Proxima demo unit today, 800-287-8533. 
<p>
<B>Free Technical Support.</B><p> 
<font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> offers unlimited free technical support and extended support hours for all our easy-to-use products. So you and your customers can rest assured that "the show will go on."
<p>
<B>CD-ROM Product Information and Demonstrations.</B><p> 
<font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> CD-ROM is a quick, dependable reference and demonstration tool for <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> entire range of products. It's the easy way to learn more about the desktop projection market and create desktop projection solutions. The CD-ROM also includes detailed information on <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Corporation, it's technology development and Dealer Sales Support Programs.
<p> 
<B>Monthly Communications and Helpful Sales Tips.</B><p> 
