<A HREF="partnering_pc.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/partnering_header.gif" border = none width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP  alt = "Resellers Forum"></A>
<p>
<font color = "236F23"><H2>Free, No-Risk, 10-Day Evaluation Program.</H2></font>
<p>
<table width = 596>
	<tr>
		<td><H3>Go ahead and try it. You've got nothing to lose.</H3>
<font size = "+1">Proxima's free, 10-day product evaluation program lets you demonstrate any of our <A HREF="../Solutions/solutions.html">Multimedia Projection<font size = "-2"><sup>TM</sup></font> products</A> with absolutely no risk. There's nothing like a hands-on trial to spark demand and help you close more sales.
<p>
<H3>It's not only free. It's easy.</H3>

Here's all you have to do to receive a Proxima product for a free 10-day evaluation period:
<OL>
<LI>Print out and complete the information requested on <B><A HREF="form.html">this form</A></B> and FAX back to Proxima</font>
<p>
Attn:  Distribution Sales Department
<br>
FAX to (619) 457-8542 or (619) 457-9647
<p>
<font size = "+1">
<LI>You'll receive a program application to complete and FAX back to Proxima.  Your completed program agreement will be submitted to order processing on the day it is received.<p>
<LI>Call your Proxima sales representative at 800-447-7692 to confirm ship dates and to get full details on how to make your product demonstration more effective.
</OL>
<p>
Because this program has been so successful, some products have a 2-3 week lead time. All products are shipped two day service. <A HREF="offers.html">Proxima's VIPs receive priority processing</A>.
<p>
Reseller agrees that the provided product will be used only in accordance with the applicable Proxima specifications and only for the purpose of testing and/or sales demonstrations. PRODUCT WILL NOT BE SHIPPED TO THE END USER.
<p>
For further information and questions call 800-447-7692.
<p>
