<TITLE>The New Ovation+ 944 Makes High-Res Projection Affordable!</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor="FFFFFF" vlink="AF0040" alink="04BC04">

<center>
<A HREF="hot_products.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/new_products_header.gif" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP  border = none alt = "New Products"></A>
<p>
<H2>The <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Ovation+ 944 makes high-resolution<br>projection portable - and affordable</H2>
</center>

<IMG SRC="gifs/ovation944.gif" align = right width = 252 height = 187>
<font size = "+2"><B>W</B></font><font size = "+1">HEN you need to present high-resolution workstation images in the office or on the road, the <font color = "FF0000">Proxima&#174;</font> Ovation&#174;+ 944 is your solution. This notebook-sized panel is quick to set up and easy to use with most workstations, PCs and Macintosh computers. With the <A HREF="../Solutions/proxima.cgi?template=item.html&item=944&sction=Description">Proxima Ovation+ 944</A> you can always depend on bright, 24-bit color images. Anytime you need to share precise, high-resolution images-CAD/CAM drawings, GIS visuals, 3D models, or entire detailed spreadsheets-the <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Ovation+ 944 delivers your computer image with the same crispness that appears on your monitor. It supports resolutions from 640 x 480 to 1280 x 1024. The Fit-to-View feature allows you to zoom up your VGA images for full-screen XGA viewing at 1024 x 768. It also intelligently scales down EWS (1280 x 1024) images while preserving the integrity and quality of the image.
<p>
<center>
<table border = 4>
	<tr>
		<td align = center><font size = "+1">&#160Download a <A HREF="ova944.pdf"><IMG SRC="gifs/pdf_logo.gif" width = 28 height = 31 border = none></A> file of the new <A HREF="ova944.pdf">Ovation+ 944 datasheet</A>! </td>
	</tr>
