<B>With the <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Ovation+ 944, you can show the "big picture."</B>
<p>
<IMG SRC="jpgs/ova944.jpg" width = 450 height = 357>
<p>
<B>Features</B>
<p>
<UL>
<LI>Compatible with all popular PCs, Macintosh computers and workstations including Sun, SGI and HP, providing the broadest compatibility range in the industry
<LI>Highly transmissive active-matrix LCD produces exceptionally bright images
<LI>Fit-to-View feature for full-screen viewing of images from 640 x 480 to 1280 x 1024
<LI>Full-resolution, fast panning across images larger than 1024 x 768
<LI>Optional <A HREF="../Solutions/proxima.cgi?template=item.html&item=DP2060/2050&sction=Description">Cyclops&#174; interactive pointer</A> system for precise, point-and-click control from the projected image
<LI>Integrated stereo audio and video supporting worldwide standards
<LI>LightBoard tool for highlighting and drawing on projected image
