<HEAD>
<TITLE>Rent A Proxima - Own Your Audience</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor="FFFFFF" vlink="AF0040" alink="04BC04">

<center>
<A HREF="hot_special.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/special_header.gif" width = 600 height = 114 border = none  ISMAP  alt = "Special Offers"></A>
</center>

<p>
<br>
<IMG SRC="../Solutions/Special/gifs/rent3.gif" align = left hspace = 18><font size = "+1"><B>Up to 50% of your first-day rental fee could be<br>applied toward a future <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> purchase!</B></font>
<br clear = all>
<br>

<center>
<table width = 600>
	<tr>
		<td width = 212 align = center valign = top><A HREF="jpgs/rent1.jpg"><IMG SRC="../Solutions/Special/gifs/rent1.gif" border = none width = 212 height = 180></A><H2>Rent A Proxima</H2></td>
		<td width = 206 align = center valign = top><br><H3>The <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> On Call<br>Rental Program.<p>For the multimedia projector you need.<br>When you need it.</H3></td>
		<td width = 182 align = center valign = top><A HREF="jpgs/rent2.jpg"><IMG SRC="../Solutions/Special/gifs/rent2.gif" border = none width = 182 height = 180></A><H2>Own Your Audience</H2></td>
	</tr>
</table>
<br>
<table width = 588>
	<tr>
		<td><p><font size = "+1"><B>The <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> On Call Rental Program</B> gives you:
<UL>
<LI>Next-day service - Delivery within 24 hours of your call
<LI>Local service and support
<LI>PC and Macintosh compatibility
<LI>A wide variety of projectors and panels to choose from
<LI>Expert advice on choosing the projector or panel that's right for you
</UL>
<br>
<font color = "2020BF"><H2>Multimedia</H2></font>
<font size = "+1">Dynamic, multimedia presentations are a phone call away.<p>
Give your presentations impact with the <B><font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> On Call Rental Program</B>! With <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font>, you can use the power of your computer to project images, make changes, highlight important points, and communicate like never before!
<p>
There's a <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> multimedia projector for <A HREF="../Solutions/solutions.html">every meeting environment</A>. The multimedia projector of your choice can be at your office in less than 24 hours!  It's that easy!
<p>
<br><font color = "2020BF"><H2>Rentals</H2></font>
<font size = "+1">Featured <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Multimedia Projection Products:
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="../Solutions/performance2.html">Ovation+ Panels</A>.  Ultra-portable and lightweight, perfect for large or small audiences.
<LI>Proxima <A HREF="../Solutions/proxima.cgi?template=item.html&item=DP2810&sction=Description">Desktop Projector 2810</A>. Exceptionally bright images for use in fully-lit meeting rooms.
<LI>Proxima <A HREF="../Solutions/proxima.cgi?template=item.html&item=DP4100z&sction=Description">Desktop Projector 4100z</A>.  Professional-quality images and photo-realistic color suited to the high profile presentation.
<LI>Proxima <A HREF="../Solutions/proxima.cgi?template=item.html&item=DP5500&sction=Description">Desktop Projector 5500</A>.
</UL>
Clear, bright images are just a phone call away!
<p>
Call <B>1-800-447-7692 ext. 415</B> today for the <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> dealer nearest you.
