<font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> is a registered trademark of <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Corporation.  Desktop Projector is a trademark of Proxima 
Corporation.  Digital Flipchart is a trademark of Tegrity, Inc. All other trademarks and registered trademarks are property of their respective owners.
