<HEAD>
<TITLE>Proxima Sells Newpoint Subsidiary</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor="FFFFFF" vlink="AF0040" alink="04BC04">

<center>
<A HREF="hot_releases.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/press_header.gif" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP  border = none alt = "Press Releases"></A>
</center>

<table width = 100%>
	<tr>
		<td align = right>For more information contact:<br>
Carol Foster, The Townsend Agency<br>
(619) 457-4888<br>
or<br>
Todd Savitt, Investor Relations<br>
(619) 457-5500 x1208<br></td>
	</tr>
</table>

<center>
<H2><font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Corporation Announces the<br>Sale of its Newpoint Subsidiary</H2>
</center>

SAN DIEGO -- June 28, 1996 -- <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Corporation (NASDAQ:PRXM) today announced the sale of its Newpoint Corporation power   
protection business to Wisconsin-based Fiskars, Inc. in a cash transaction totaling approximately $7 million.
<p>
"The sale of the Newpoint business reflects <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> strategy to put all of our management focus on the fast-growing multimedia projection industry," stated John Rehfeld, President and Chief Executive Officer of <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Corporation.  "Although Newpoint's power protection business is at an all-time high, this sale will provide additional financial resources that can be used to meet the challenges and opportunities that face our projection business."
<p>
Fiskars, Inc. is a world leader in the manufacturing, sale, and distribution of a wide range of consumer products for the home, school, and office.
<p>
<font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> is a leading developer, manufacturer, and marketer of multimedia projection products which bring the power of the computer to the workgroup.  These systems increase the productivity and effectiveness of business meetings, interactive workgroup sessions, training, and computer-based presentations.
<p>

<center>
[&#160 <A HREF="../University/university.html">Presenters University</A>&#160 |&#160 <A HREF="../Solving/solving.html">Support And Service</A>&#160 |&#160 
<A HREF="../Partnering/partnering.html">Resellers Forum</A>&#160 ]
