<DOCHDR>
http://intergate.prxm.com:80/University/School/entries5.html 205.163.25.34 19970209104620 text/html 5132
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 10:46:27 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
