<HEAD>

<TITLE>Product Maintenance - Panels</TITLE>

</HEAD>



<BODY bgcolor = "#ffffff">



<center>

<A HREF="solving.map"><IMG SRC="jpgs/header.jpg" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP border = none alt = "Support And Services"></A>
</center>



<HR>



<H3>Panel Maintenance</H3>



<HR>



<P>

<I>Cleaning the Protective Glass</I> 

<P>

To clean the top or bottom protective glass, put a small amount

of glass cleaner on a soft cloth or lens cleaning tissue. Gently

wipe the glass plate to remove any accumulated dust or grit.

<P>

<I>Temperature Extremes</I> 

<P>

Liquid crystals will freeze at low temperatures. There's no harm

in this. If your panel is ever exposed to extremely cold temperatures,

allow it to warm to room temperature before use.

<P>



<center>
[&#160 <A HREF="../University/university.html">Presenters University</A>&#160 |&#160<!A HREF="solving.html">Support And Service<!/A>&#160 |&#160<A HREF="../Partnering/partnering.html">Resellers Forum</A>&#160 ]<br>[&#160 
<A HREF="../New/new.html">What's Hot</A>&#160 |&#160 <A HREF="../Solutions/index.html">Proxima Products</A>&#160 |&#160<A HREF="../About/about.html">About Proxima</A>&#160 ]<p>[&#160 <A HREF="../home.html">Home Page</A>&#160 ]
<br>
</center>

