<A HREF="hot_products.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/new_products_header.gif" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP  border = none alt = "New Products"></A>
<p>
<H2>The Desktop Projector 5500 projects the<br>
biggest, brightest multimedia images.</H2>
</center>

<IMG SRC="gifs/proj5500.gif" align=right width = 245 height = 180 hspace=5>
<font size = "+2"><B>T</B></font><font size = "+1">HE <font color = "FF0000">Proxima&#174;</font> Desktop Projector 5500 projects color images at 500 ANSI lumens-making it the brightest projector in its class. It displays images that are up to 30 feet diagonally. Colors are vivid and fully-saturated and the images are exceptionally sharp. Even the biggest images do not appear washed out, faded, or fuzzy. And, a brightly lit room is never a worry.
<p>
With an appealing mix of standard features, the <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Desktop Projector 5500 offers exceptional-quality multimedia projection in one convenient package. The <A HREF="../Solutions/proxima.cgi?template=item.html&item=DP5500&sction=Description">Desktop Projector 5500</A> includes two computer and two video inputs which make it simple to connect multiple presenters. This VGA projector can also handle SVGA images, giving it wider computer compatibility. Its motorized zoom lens lets you position the projector anywhere in the room. The 1.6:1 range of this lens is the widest available on any projector in its class. This provides greater flexibility not only in placement, but in image size and therefore audience size. The Desktop Projector 5500 also includes a remote that makes controlling your presentation easy. It has zoom and focus buttons, as well as a "joystick" which provides mouse-like control of the PC computer.
<p>
