<LI>16.7 million colors to make your presentation true to your computer image
<LI>Multiple computer and video inputs accommodate multiple presenters
<LI>Supports SVGA computer images for wider computer compatibility
<LI>Motorized 1.6:1 zoom lens for flexible placement anywhere in the room
<LI>Easy control from the cordless remote with mouse-like "joystick" and zoom and focus buttons
