<HEAD>
<TITLE>PROXIMA REDUCES PRICES UP TO 21 PERCENT</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor="FFFFFF" vlink="AF0040" alink="04BC04">

<center>
<A HREF="hot_releases.map"><IMG SRC="gifs/press_header.gif" width = 600 height = 114  ISMAP  border = none alt = "Press Releases"></A>
<H2><font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> reduces prices up to 21 percent on <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font><br>Ovation and Proxima Ovation+ LCD panels</H2>
<H3>Strengthens Price Leadership Position<br>
in Desktop Projection Market</H3>
</center>

San Diego, Calif., March 15, 1996 -- <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Corporation (NASDAQ:PRXM) today reduced prices on its <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Ovation and Proxima Ovation+ LCD panels, strengthening its position as the leading provider of reliable and affordable desktop projection solutions.
<p>
The lower list prices, which are effective immediately, apply to five of   
the company's seven LCD panel models.  Today's announcement places <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> panels 15 to 20 percent below comparable competitive LCD panels.
<p>
"Our customers expect <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> LCD panels to provide full-color, active-matrix projection solutions for a wide range of applications," said Terry Hicks, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> product line manager.  "With today's announcement, we are strengthening our position as the price/performance leader in offering desktop projection solutions at the best value."
<p>
Capable of projecting both computer and video images onto a large screen, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> LCD panels are widely used for sales and mobile presentations, workgroup productivity, training and education, video conferencing and multimedia presentations.
<p>
The <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Ovation+ family delivers unsurpassed image quality and 24-bit processing, 16.7 million colors, and up to 800 x 600 (S-VGA) resolution.    It features superior video capability and a remarkable LightBoard annotation  tool. The <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Ovation family offers the best value in active-matrix LCD projection panels. It displays up to 2 million colors and possesses the most extensive list of features in its class, including a programmable remote control. Both the <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Ovation+ and <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> Ovation series offer the optional Cyclops cordless mouse pointer, which enhances interaction between the user and the audience.
<p>
The new U.S. suggested retail prices are as follows:

<pre>
	Model 			PercentDecrease 	Former List Price 	New List Price
Proxima Ovation 810     	21%     		$3,295      		$2,595
Proxima Ovation 820     	18%     		$3,695      		$2,995
Proxima Ovation+ 840     	11%     		$4,495      		$3,995
Proxima Ovation+ 842     	10%     		$4,995			$4,495
Proxima Ovation+ 846     	16%     		$5,995      		$4,995
</pre>
<p>
 Headquartered in San Diego, California, <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> is a leading developer, manufacturer and marketer of desktop projection products, which increase the productivity and effectiveness of business meetings, interactive   
workgroup sessions, training and computer-based presentations.  The company's broad line of products includes the Desktop Projector family, the <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font>  Ovation and Ovation+ lines of LCD projection panels and <font color = "FF0000">Proxima's</font> Cyclops interactive pointer system.
<p>
 Dealers and VARs who purchase through distribution can either contact   
their distributor of choice or call <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> at 1-800-447-7694.  End users can contact their nearest authorized <font color = "FF0000">Proxima</font> dealer.
<p>

