<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Robert Gilman - The Changing Patterns Of Community</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<H3><CENTER>A cultural history from tribes to cities .. and beyond</CENTER>
</H3>
<HR><BR>
<P><CENTER>Originally published in <A HREF="TOC01.htm"><CITE>IN CONTEXT
</CITE>#1</A>, Winter 1983, Page 33<BR>
